---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import List from "@/components/ui/List.astro";
---

<Layout title="Research | Anna Yaghobová">
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Research Statement</h1>

    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        My research focuses on students’ preconceptions about digital systems and on connecting these findings with school practice. I am particularly interested in how learners understand abstract computing concepts, such as the internet, computer systems, hardware components, and operating systems, and how these ideas can inform the design of meaningful teaching materials. Now I am also working on how usinf AI can enhance classroom practice.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        In my work, I combine empirical research on students’ thinking with the development and evaluation of instructional materials for lower secondary education. My aim is to support teaching that builds on students’ existing ideas in the sense of educational reconstruction.
      </p>
    </div>

    <List listTitle="Current Projects" listItems={[
      {
        title: "Project title",
        type: "Project type, role, years",
        link: "",
        linkname: "",
        description: "Short description of the project. Replace this placeholder with information about an ongoing research project, dissertation work, collaboration, grant, or development of teaching materials."
      },
      {
        title: "Project title",
        type: "Project type, role, years",
        link: "",
        linkname: "",
        description: "Short description of another current project. You can duplicate or remove these items as needed."
      }
    ]} />

    <List listTitle="Past Projects" listItems={[
      {
        title: "Project title",
        type: "Project type, role, years",
        link: "",
        linkname: "",
        description: "Short description of a completed project. Replace this placeholder with information about a finished research project, thesis, publication-related project, or completed teaching-material development."
      },
      {
        title: "Project title",
        type: "Project type, role, years",
        link: "",
        linkname: "",
        description: "Short description of another past project. You can duplicate or remove these items as needed."
      }
    ]} />

  </div>
</Layout>                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d={RESEARCH_ICONS[area.field as keyof typeof RESEARCH_ICONS]?.path || RESEARCH_ICONS['computer-science'].path}
                />
              </svg>
            </BetterIcon>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{area.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-base">{area.description}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>

    <List listTitle="Current Projects" listItems={[
      {
        title: "Radioactivity Studies",
        description: "Investigation of radioactive properties in uranium minerals and isolation of new radioactive elements."
      },
      {
        title: "Measurement Techniques",
        description: "Development of precise methods for measuring radioactive emissions and their properties."
      }
    ]} />

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Research Impact</h2>
    <p class="text-lg mb-6">
      My research has opened new frontiers in radioactivity studies, leading to practical applications in both scientific research and medical treatments. The discoveries have revolutionized our understanding of atomic structure and radioactive decay processes.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
